          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Ratios of gamma peak areas were measured for different",
                "thickness of sample :",
                "Thickness   Gamma416/Gamma336   Gamma416/Gamma391",
                "  micron       x10**2             x10",
                "   10       2.64 +- 0.60         2.45 +- 0.60",
                "   20       2.84 +- 0.58         2.63 +- 0.58",
                "   40       2.99 +- 0.47         3.03 +- 0.50",
                "   90       3.40 +- 0.24         3.65 +- 0.27",
                "  100       3.71 +- 0.14         3.85 +- 0.17",
                "  160       4.22 +- 0.21         4.57 +- 0.27",
                "  200       4.27 +- 0.15         4.50 +- 0.16",
                "  400       4.50 +- 0.20         4.78 +- 0.25",
                "To determine cross section for (n,gamma) reaction",
                "one needs to multiple column 2 data by (0.511+-0.051)",
                "and column 3 data by (0.479+-0.038).",
                "The true value of cross section was determined by",
                "extrapolation of the data from this table to zero",
                "thickness by least square method and by formula given",
                "on page 196 taking into account contribution of",
                "secondary neutrons from samples and construction",
                "materials and secondary neutrons absorption in sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
